        "action": "Increase the amount of entitled breaks employees are allowed on a shift.",
        "additional_details": "I would also want parliament to increase uninterrupted breaks in a 12 hour shift every 3 hours. So every employee gets 3 uninterrupted breaks every 3 hours in a 12 hour shift.",
